tist)|Richard Slee]] *[[Martin Smith (potter)|Martin Smith]] *[[Rupert Spira]] *[[Julian Stair]] *[[William Staite Murray]] *[[Angus Suttie]] *[[Geoffrey Swindell]] *[[James Tower]] *[[Marianne de Trey]]<ref name="vads.ac.uk">The inspiration of Marianne de Trey – necessity and decoration from cloth to clay: [http://www.vads.ac.uk/learning/csc/detrey/essay.html VADS: the online resource for visual arts - The inspiration of Marianne de Trey – necessity and decoration from cloth to clay], accessdate: May 29, 2016</ref> *[[Judith Trim]] *[[Edmund de Waal|Edmund De Waal]] *[[Alan Wallwork]] *[[Peter Wright (ceramicist)|Peter Wright]] *[[Takeshi Yasuda]] }}
